(change-comment "We grab another 1 literal by clicking on the LITERAL button again...")
(mouse-sequence m 37 130 m 40 140 m 50 172 m 62 184 m 72 212 m 100 244 m 110 272 m 138 304 m 166 336 m 178 368 m 206 400 m 216 428 m 228 464 m 240 476 m 244 479 m 246 480 m 247 484 m 250 494 m 254 497 m 257 499 m 258 500 m 259 500 m 260 501 m 261 502 m 262 503 m 263 503 m 263 506 m 264 509 m 267 513 m 271 516 m 274 519 m 276 529 m 279 532 m 281 534 m 282 535 m 284 539 m 287 543 m 289 545 m 290 546 m 291 547 m 293 549 m 294 551 m 295 552 m 296 553 m 297 554 m 298 555 m 299 557 m 300 558 m 300 559 m 301 561 m 302 562 m 302 563 c 302 563)
