(mouse-sequence m 57 118 m 56 116 m 55 114 m 53 111 m 50 108 m 48 106 m 46 105 m 45 104 m 44 102 m 44 100 m 44 98 m 43 97 m 42 95 m 41 94 m 40 93 m 39 92 m 39 91 m 39 90 m 38 90 c 38 90)
